data.description: This delightful home with three bedrooms and two bathrooms is situated in the charming Acadia Oaks Subdivision. Recently updated with features like fresh paint, new hardware, and LED lights, this property is ready for immediate occupancy. The residence showcases an appealing exterior, highlighted by stained wood siding on the front porch, arched windows with shutters, an accent wall, decorative landscaping, and a covered carport. It also comes with a stainless steel refrigerator, microwave, & dishwasher, and two flat-screen televisions & hot tub. Nestled in Acadia Oaks Subdivision and conveniently positioned in Oak Grove, the home provides easy access to the Longleaf Elementary which is in the Oak Grove School District and near many places such as Turtle Creek Mall and several eateries.
